OL,3,CVisa and TikTok launch 'creator card'
OL,4,Cto support entrepreneurs
OL,6,FVisa has partnered with TikTok to
OL,7,Flaunch a debit card designed for
OL,8,Fcontent creators.
OL,10,FThose behind the launch said it
OL,11,Fsupports the UK's "fast-growing"
OL,12,Fcreator economy and is designed to
OL,13,Fgive people access to financial tools
OL,14,Fto run and grow their business.
OL,16,FThe new creator card has features
OL,17,Fdesigned to improve cash flow, Visa
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,26,@sD@SOUsD@`O]
