OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776731804
OL,3,CVisa and TikTok launch 'creator card'
OL,4,Cto support entrepreneurs
OL,6,FDuring a TikTok Live, creators may be
OL,7,Frewarded for their creativity through
OL,8,Fvirtual gifts. Creators can then
OL,9,Fconvert the value of gifts and they
OL,10,Fmay be exchanged for income.
OL,12,FVisa and TikTok's creator card and
OL,13,Fbusiness account enable creators to
OL,14,Faccess earnings faster and avoid
OL,15,Fdelays from waiting for payouts to
OL,16,Ffully clear, those behind the
OL,17,Finitiative said.
OL,19,FThe creator card went through a "soft
OL,20,Flaunch" trial period and is now being
OL,21,Frolled out.
OL,26,@{D@aOU|D@GO]
