OL,3,CVisa and TikTok launch 'creator card'
OL,4,Cto support entrepreneurs
OL,6,FLucy Demery, senior vice president,
OL,7,Fhead of Visa Commercial Solutions,
OL,8,FEurope, said: "We are incredibly
OL,9,Fexcited to launch the UK creator card
OL,10,Fwith TikTok to empower the next
OL,11,Fgeneration of entrepreneurs in the
OL,12,Fdigital economy.
OL,14,F"This launch is designed to give
OL,15,Fcreators faster access to income from
OL,16,FTikTok Live, brand partnerships, and
OL,17,Fplatform payouts, so they can spend,
OL,18,Fplan and reinvest in their business
OL,19,Fstraight away."
OL,26,@pD@OOUvD@AOU{D@OO]
