OL,3,CVisa and TikTok launch 'creator card'
OL,4,Cto support entrepreneurs
OL,6,FPaula D'Urbano, country manager,
OL,7,FTikTok Live UK, Ireland and Baltics,
OL,8,Fsaid: "TikTok Live is creating the
OL,9,Fnext generation of digital
OL,10,Fentrepreneurs, transforming the way
OL,11,Fcreators and audiences connect in real-
OL,12,Ftime.
OL,14,F"By partnering with Visa, we're giving
OL,15,Fthe Live community even more ways to
OL,16,Fmanage their rewards ` helping
OL,17,Fcreators to turn their passion into a
OL,18,Fsustainable career."
