OL,3,CVisa and TikTok launch 'creator card'
OL,4,Cto support entrepreneurs
OL,6,FA survey commissioned by Visa
OL,7,Findicated that nearly half (49%) of
OL,8,Fcontent creators feel that late or
OL,9,Finconsistent payments have impacted
OL,10,Ftheir ability to run their business
OL,11,Fand two-fifths (41%) have had to turn
OL,12,Fdown new opportunities due to cash
OL,13,Fflow issues.
OL,15,FThe survey was carried out by
OL,16,FCensuswide, among 1,000 professional
OL,17,Fcontent creators across the UK on
OL,18,Fmultiple platforms. The research was
OL,19,Fcarried out between March and June.
